{"tid":2321874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲人真係唔適合做聆聽者","createTime":"2020-12-12T01:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T10:43:08.000Z","uid":103263,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2cb5fe6891abbe0e0214e9f8235f31d3059ad725","tid":2321874,"uid":103263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:09:09.000Z","msg":"有時同朋友講開最近忙緊啲咩，辛苦緊啲咩，句嘢都未埋尾，佢已經搶疆 &quot;唉，我仲忙過你/我仲辛苦過你啦，呢輪做緊xxxx&quot;下刪一萬字<br />\n<br />\n真係屌你老母，家陣係你聽緊我講定係你自己想講，呢啲位唔使好似考oral咁衝晒出黎架。你係想噴嘅，都應該等人講埋先吖。而家講出黎好似好撚on9,但又不吐不快，唔講出黎真係頂撚住"},{"pid":"33c20f7d78ac0f472fdd74d2e16af756dc73f91c","tid":2321874,"uid":172443,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:15:08.000Z","msg":"同咁自私嘅人都有fd做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然9成人都係咁"},{"pid":"460a7e061870ab13fe1300072fed6c6d83b18f7e","tid":2321874,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:24:02.000Z","msg":"公司大把呢啲撚屌<br />\n<br />\n諗住呻下自己好多嘢做兼趕住放貨就以為人地推卸責任比佢做<br />\n<br />\n一句撻埋嚟話：我都好多嘢做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8fe2018eb3eec306e9c219f62a41fd5da20727","tid":2321874,"uid":63037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:33:39.000Z","msg":"呢啲人真係好自我中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔明點解會有朋友"},{"pid":"5efd5df50aaa7ab904fcb6d41abaae8627fb2e5c","tid":2321874,"uid":147780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:38:26.000Z","msg":"真，有時想呻下自己啲唔開心嘅嘢<br />\n一句撻過黎話下？你果啲算係乜，我仲大壓力喎<br />\n然後就變咗聽佢呻<br />\n<br />\n我心諗，明明搵得人講，即係我本身有少少負能量架啦，點知轉個頭變成情緒收集箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要比較，話我果啲濕濕碎，做乜嘢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bfb3475f68d41411f70f0bcd8f99678ef4e331","tid":2321874,"uid":103263,